rows.label: qst101104_msg0003
rows.name:
My dad's waiting, so I'll head
back to town right away.

rows.label: qst101104_msg0004
rows.name:
Yeah! I wrapped a cloth
around my ankle, so I
think I can walk somehow.

rows.label: qst101104_msg0005
rows.name:
I think my dad will give you some
kind of reward, so when you get back
to town, please come to our house.

rows.label: qst101104_msg0101
rows.name: Ow... Oh! The Confusion Ivy person!

rows.label: qst101104_msg0102
rows.name:
Hmm... I pushed myself too hard
walking, so my ankle's swollen...

rows.label: qst101104_msg0301
rows.name: You brought me Gulan Walnut! Thank you!

rows.label: qst101104_msg0302
rows.name:
The pain in my ankle finally
went away, and I can stand now.
